Events
Our
Events
Miami Food Trucks Events,
is the coolest truck festival in the city of Miami. This is a family event that we hold every day of the week, from Monday to Saturday, in different parts of the city of Miami. Where you and your family can enjoy the most varied gastronomic offer on wheels in the city. Our food selections include:
American, Mexican, Italian, Argentinian, Mediterranean, French, Asian, Venezuelan,
seafood, smoothies or other drinks, desserts and much more.
In addition, we have activities and games so that your children have as much fun as possible.
Weekly free
